        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main id="top">
    <div class="container" style="margin-top:20px;">
      <div id="successBanner" class="line-safe" style="display:none; background:#d4edda; padding:14px; border-radius:12px; margin-bottom:10px;">
        Your application was submitted successfully. We’ll be in touch soon.
      </div>
    </div>
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container hero-grid">
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow">Hamsa Nomads retreat stay</div>
          <h1>A warm, beautiful home base near Mt. Snow.</h1>
          <p class="lead">A one-page GitHub-friendly landing page for a Hamsa Nomads retreat at The Birch villa in Dover, Vermont — with the property photos, the imperfect traveling line, and all the overview information except sign-up and booking.</p>
          <div class="pill-row">
            <div class="pill">Dover, Vermont</div>
            <div class="pill">Near Mt. Snow</div>
            <div class="pill">Pool + hot tub</div>
            <div class="pill">Kitchen + laundry</div>
            <div class="pill">Pet friendly</div>
          </div>

          <div style="margin-top:18px;">
            <a href="apply.html" class="button">Apply Now</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-card line-safe">
          <div class="hero-cta">
            <a href="apply.html" class="button">Apply Now</a>
          </div>
          <img class="hero-image" src="https://media.vrbo.com/lodging/103000000/102120000/102116300/102116254/c3850734.jpg?impolicy=resizecrop&ra=fit&rw=598" alt="Dining and gathering area at the Birch villa" />
          <div class="hero-caption">A light-filled shared space that immediately feels like a retreat: warm wood, long tables, and room to gather, eat, and talk.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="stay">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header line-safe">
          <div>
            <div class="eyebrow">At a glance</div>
            <h2>The stay</h2>
          </div>
          <p>The property is presented as a beautiful group house rather than a generic rental. The site stays editorial and calm, while the hand-drawn line gives it that slightly incorrect, human Hamsa Nomads touch.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="info-grid">
          <article class="info-card">
            <div class="meta-label">Property</div>
            <div class="meta-value">The Birch villa, a large private home used as the base for the retreat.</div>
          </article>
          <article class="info-card">
            <div class="meta-label">Area</div>
            <div class="meta-value">Dover, Vermont, about two minutes from Mt. Snow, with river and mountain access nearby.</div>
          </article>
          <article class="info-card">
            <div class="meta-label">Amenities</div>
            <div class="meta-value">Indoor pool, hot tub, kitchen, washer, dryer, and game room energy built into the property.</div>
          </article>
          <article class="info-card">
            <div class="meta-label">Who it’s for</div>
            <div class="meta-value">Jewish young adults, couples, and a few families looking for a social, warm, observance-aware retreat experience.</div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="gallery">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header line-safe">
          <div>
            <div class="eyebrow">Use the actual place</div>
            <h2>Property gallery</h2>
          </div>
          <p>The page now uses photos from the real listing: the shared dining space, a bedroom, the pool, and the game room. The line stays above the page, but never crosses the images.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="gallery-grid">
          <article class="gallery-card tall line-safe">
            <img src="https://media.vrbo.com/lodging/103000000/102120000/102116300/102116254/c3850734.jpg?impolicy=resizecrop&ra=fit&rw=598" alt="Dining area at the villa" />
          </article>
          <article class="gallery-card line-safe">
            <img src="https://media.vrbo.com/lodging/103000000/102120000/102116300/102116254/8ec616cc.jpg?impolicy=resizecrop&ra=fit&rw=297" alt="Bedroom at the villa" />
          </article>
          <article class="gallery-card line-safe">
            <img src="https://media.vrbo.com/lodging/103000000/102120000/102116300/102116254/f5cf3a4a.jpg?impolicy=resizecrop&ra=fit&rw=297" alt="Indoor pool at the villa" />
          </article>
          <article class="gallery-card line-safe">
            <img src="https://media.vrbo.com/lodging/103000000/102120000/102116300/102116254/d07ff8bb.jpg?impolicy=resizecrop&ra=fit&rw=297" alt="Game room at the villa" />
